text: Go DoJaeJung! Carol Medley is here. Jaehyun's voice carols the most imo and he stood out so much. He always talks about his love for winter and the holiday season and itâ€™s such a beautiful way for him to express that. It's so fitting that he starts off this Christmas Carol Medley as someone who loves the holiday season and his warm voice is so distinguishable.... Not to mention he's such a talented vocalist who's one of the very best in NCT! His lows here, his highs, his mids and those gorgeous runs. This year he has shown so many sides of himself in music, from performing his self written and composed Lost on tour, to his very own solo song Forever Only, as well as gifting fans his very own cover of Can't Take My Eyes Off You. His musical colour is very recognisable at this point - If there's anything classic or jazzy - Jaehyun definitely owns that. Born to be Singer JAEHYUN. Everyone did a great job in this! <3 Happy Holidays to everyone watching too ğŸ„
